mapping.ptr being uint64_t sounds incorrect. It's not a fault in this 
code but rutabaga_ffi. Please review rutabaga_ffi and correct it if 
appropriate.

> +        memory_region_add_subregion(&g->parent_obj.hostmem,
> +                                    mblob.offset, mr);
